DarkMouse::
She sat up to the security console and kept an eye on things.  She 
saw the new controls and liked the upgrades.  She was in the matrix 
with her computers around her.  She checked the scanners and 
frequencies.  She tried to pick up on the maximal calls, but nothing 
came it.  She sat back in the chair, put her feet up on the console, 
her hands behind her back and leaned back in the chair.  She was in 
utter delight.
